properties.credit: Lake and River Water Level products are generated by the Global Land Service of Copernicus, the Earth Observation Programme of the European Commission and the Theia-land program supported by CNES. The research leading to the current version of the product has received funding from CNES, LEGOS, IRD and CLS.
properties.purpose: This product is first designed to fit the requirements of the Global Land component of Land Service of Copernicus. It can be also useful for all applications related to the environment monitoring, climate research and hydrology.
